H3.text: What was the first name of the Dutch explorer, Tasman, after whom Tasmania is named. ABEL

A4.text: Abel Janszoon Tasman (Dutch: [ˈaːbəl ˈjɑnsoːn ˈtɑsmɑn]; 1603 – 10 October 1659) was a Dutch seafarer and explorer
